arts.ttl: Valencia-Real Oviedo clash postponed due to weather warnings
arts.sum: Valencia and Real Oviedo were due to lock horns on Monday night to close out La Liga’s Matchday 7 slate, but the two sides will have to find an alternate date to play the match at Mestalla after it was postponed on Monday. arts.ttl: Valencia vs. Real Oviedo postponed due to risk of torrential rain and floods
arts.sum: The LALIGA Matchday 7 game between Valencia and Real Oviedo at Mestalla, scheduled for this Monday, has been postponed until Tuesday due to a red alert for the risk of torrential rain and flooding in the province of Valencia.
